               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Ṣalot za-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝna Māryām ba-Dabra Golgotā, Prayer of Our Lady Mary
                     on Mount Golgotha on the 21st of Sane (fols. 1r-41v)
 II) Malkǝʾa ʾIyasus
                     Krǝstos “Image of Jesus Christ” (fols. 42r-51r) (ChRep 343, no. 269)
 III)
                     ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... "I worship Thee..." (fols. 52r-55r) (ChRep 318,
                     no. 338)
 IV) Ṣalot baʾǝnta bǝʿǝr wa-lāhm, ʾAsmat-prayer for protecting the
                     cattle (fols. 56v-60v).</summary>

               </msContents>
